lule.hunkar.provincesofcanada

Class Province

  • java.lang.Object
    • lule.hunkar.provincesofcanada.Province

  • public class Province
extends java.lang.Object
    Province class creates specified province object. It has two constructors one of them creates province object with default values. Other one creates province objects with specified values. It provides method to print the details of a province object as a string.
    Author:
    Hunkar Lule
